skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: big sur marathon fan
des: The Big Sur International Marathon is an annual marathon held in California, United States along the Pacific coast. This Alexa Skill enables you to get facts about the marathon and get all the information needed to have a great running experience, before, during and after the marathon. This skill is not sponsored or endorsed by Big Sur International Marathon.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
